Five In Row authors and contributors
====================================

Local project
-------------

The original 5inRow C engine and repository-specific integration work belong to
this repository's contributors.

Rapfi upstream
--------------

This branch includes V6 source code under engine/v6-core, imported from
https://github.com/dhbloo/rapfi.git.

Upstream authors and acknowledgements are preserved at:

- engine/v6-core/upstream/AUTHORS.upstream

The upstream AUTHORS file credits Haobin Duan (dblue), HZY (sigmoid), Joker2770,
crsov, nguyencongminh090, subarashikihibi, Stockfish authors, and the Pikafish
team/contributors named there.
